	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/04/16/morning-agenda-bank-of-america-posts-a-loss/" data-title="Bank of America&#8217;s Big Loss" data-description="Bank of America posts a $276 million loss. | Fed chairwoman suggests new rules for short-term borrowing. | Moelis &amp; Company faces an I.P.O. market chill. | Investors got a glimpse of Alibaba&#039;s growth in Yahoo&#039;s earnings report. | Questions about the value of corporate monitoring programs.">
